19/06/2006
SHKODRA, Albania -- A new border checkpoint in Virpazar-Shkodra -- between Albania and Montenegro -- was officially inaugurated on Sunday (18 June). Albanian Environment Minister Lufter Xhuveli and his visiting Montenegrin counterpart, Boro Vucinic, attended the ceremony in Shkodra. Earlier, the two ministers sealed a bilateral memorandum for co-operation in environmental protection and sustainable development. (Pobjeda, Albanian News - 19/06/06)
